About Event

​​​​​We're so excited to invite you back to LuxFit for an all-levels-welcome outdoor weightlifting workout!

​​​If you're looking for a way to meet like-minded people while learning a new skill or getting your workout in, this is the event for you.

​​​​​​​The 1-hour workout will be led by an amazing coach at LuxFit who has worked with athletes in the Bay for years! After the work out, we will host brunch with assorted bagel sandwiches & coffee, also in hayes valley 🥯
